{"pageProps":{"blogPost":{"id":556,"title":"Top 5 International & Indian HR Leaders To Follow In 2022","content":"<p>Our list of top 5 International and Indian HR leaders you should follow in 2022. Their opinions, ideas and thoughts have received an overwhelming response from the community and the industry. Look out for their posts and follow them on Twitter as well as LinkedIn.</p><p><strong>International</strong><br><br>- <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/ACoAAAACAAcBVexPqZ1rx-Rai3VQO9iU7FjPRDU\">Josh Bersin</a>, Corporate Talent, HR, &amp; Learning Analyst, founder of Bersin Research and Bersin Academy<br>Twitter: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Josh_Bersin\">@Josh_Bersin</a></p><p><br>- <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/ACoAAAAKZvIBrMbZJXYrLAQ_kovjelKD1AS4RGs\">Frank Sonnenberg</a>, Top 100 Thought Leaders in America<br>Twitter: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/FSonnenberg\">@FSonnenberg</a></p><p><br>- <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/ACoAAAAWae8B58ymc5bvIg2OoKh9mJj-K4hmJW0\">Meghan M. Biro</a>, CEO, <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/talentculture/\">TalentCulture - World of Work</a><br>Twitter: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/MeghanMBiro\">@MeghanMBiro</a><br><br>- <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/ACoAAAATiNEB26mikxwAO4B8P_Hjud8B3AjKxDo\">Hannah Morgan</a>, Job Strategist, <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/career-sherpa.net/\">Career Sherpa.net</a><br>Twitter: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/careersherpa\">@careersherpa</a></p><p><br>- <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/ACoAAAAJDQYBFpSM0TTZtEIANo3iaAIvQyhUwrM\">Steve Boese</a>, President &amp; Co-Founder, <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/h3hr/\">H3 HR Advisors</a><br>Twitter: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SteveBoese\">@SteveBoese</a></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Indian</strong><br><br>- <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/ACoAAAvNUlABT5JinZ9Md-p7s5j2hb99njrSZbs\">Vineet Nayar</a>, Founder Chairman and CEO, <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/sampark-foundation/\">Sampark Foundation</a>, Author of Employees First, Customers Second<br>Twitter: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/vineetnayar\">@vineetnayar</a></p><p><br>- <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/ACoAAAAASVIBp2XTUY0RUjimXyQV6iJk8cp0WhM\">Gautam Ghosh</a>, Employer Branding and Digital HR Consultant<br>Twitter: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/GautamGhosh\">@GautamGhosh</a></p><p><br>- <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/ACoAAAB3HQ8BU3NcwGPk-ukHEdWdwHgFfjCNznk\">Abhijit Bhaduri</a>, Founder of Abhijit Bhaduri &amp; Associates<br>Twitter: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/AbhijitBhaduri\">@AbhijitBhaduri</a></p><p><br>- <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/ACoAAAJKlf0B-3g4lSr-BMBEyNOG4p8dDf71KwU\">Prabir Jha</a>, Founder &amp; CEO Prabir Jha People Advisory<br>Twitter: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/PrabirJha\">@PrabirJha</a></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>- <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/ACoAAABBTtcBHK9_Hmauvw3AMhhBVQNPxB6E2Zw\">Nathan SV</a>, Chief Talent Officer at <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/deloitte/\">Deloitte</a> India<br>Twitter: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Nathansv\">@Nathansv</a></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Follow us for more:</p><p>Subscribe, Share and Like us on <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCrceycnUns21KLXYubEZuTA\">Youtube</a></p><p>Like our<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/edgenetworkspvtltd\"> Facebook</a> page:</p><p>Follow us on <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/getedge\">LinkedIn</a></p><p>Follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/getedge_ai\">Twitter</a></p><p>&nbsp;</p>","slug":"top-5-international-and-indian-hr-leaders-to-follow-in-2022","subTitle":"Who are the top 5 International & Indian HR leaders to follow in 2022? Read ahead and let us know your thoughts.","sizeInGrid":null,"meta_description":null,"metaDesc":null,"published_at":"2022-02-10T11:05:33.310Z","created_at":"2022-02-10T10:30:35.392Z","updated_at":"2022-02-10T11:05:33.582Z","featuredImage":{"id":712,"name":"Top-5-International-&-Indian-HR-Leaders-To-Follow-In-2022 v